  {
    "id": "seed-001",
    "text": "I spent 10 minutes staring at the ceiling last night, wondering if I'm the only one who does this. Then I realized everyone does. That's why we all have the same thoughts.",
    "category": "Deep",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T18:00:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-001",
    "authorName": "QuietFox72",
    "authorColor": "#FF5733",
    "replyCount": 0,
    "reactionCount": 8
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-002",
    "text": "The scariest thing about adulthood isn't paying bills. It's realizing you're becoming the person you swore you never would be.",
    "category": "Confessions",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T17:30:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-002",
    "authorName": "HappyWolf45",
    "authorColor": "#33FF57",
    "replyCount": 0,
    "reactionCount": 19
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-003",
    "text": "What if the voice in your head isn't yours? What if it's the last thought of someone who died thinking of you?",
    "category": "Late Night",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T16:45:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-003",
    "authorName": "SmartBear99",
    "authorColor": "#3357FF",
    "replyCount": 0,
    "reactionCount": 12
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-004",
    "text": "I told my therapist I have trust issues. She said 'I believe you.' I'm not sure if that was a joke or the first honest thing anyone's said to me.",
    "category": "Funny",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T15:20:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-004",
    "authorName": "SillyTiger23",
    "authorColor": "#F3FF33",
    "replyCount": 2,
    "reactionCount": 8
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-005",
    "text": "The best advice I never took: Stop trying to be happy. Just stop being unhappy. The rest will figure itself out.",
    "category": "Advice",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T14:10:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-005",
    "authorName": "WiseDragon11",
    "authorColor": "#FF33F3",
    "replyCount": 0,
    "reactionCount": 20
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-006",
    "text": "I deleted all my social media accounts yesterday. Today I feel lighter, like I lost 50 pounds of other people's opinions.",
    "category": "Confessions",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T13:05:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-006",
    "authorName": "BraveRabbit88",
    "authorColor": "#00BFFF",
    "replyCount": 0,
    "reactionCount": 18
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-007",
    "text": "2 AM thoughts hit different. The walls start talking, the shadows have opinions, and suddenly you're questioning every decision you've ever made.",
    "category": "Late Night",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T12:30:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-007",
    "authorName": "DreamyOwl77",
    "authorColor": "#7CFC00",
    "replyCount": 3,
    "reactionCount": 9
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-008",
    "text": "Money can't buy happiness. But it can buy a jetski. And have you ever seen a sad person on a jetski?",
    "category": "Funny",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T11:15:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-008",
    "authorName": "PlayfulPenguin42",
    "authorColor": "#FF8C00",
    "replyCount": 0,
    "reactionCount": 14
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-009",
    "text": "Love isn't about finding someone you can live with. It's about finding someone you can't live without. And then realizing you actually can, you just don't want to.",
    "category": "Deep",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T10:00:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-009",
    "authorName": "GentleUnicorn55",
    "authorColor": "#9932CC",
    "replyCount": 0,
    "reactionCount": 22
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-010",
    "text": "If someone tells you they have a secret and then says 'promise not to tell anyone', they've already told at least one other person. That's how secrets work.",
    "category": "Advice",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T09:25:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-010",
    "authorName": "MysteriousLynx33",
    "authorColor": "#20B2AA",
    "replyCount": 1,
    "reactionCount": 5
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-011",
    "text": "I used to think I was indecisive. But now I'm not so sure.",
    "category": "Funny",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T08:40:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-011",
    "authorName": "ChillKoala67",
    "authorColor": "#FF1493",
    "replyCount": 1,
    "reactionCount": 3
  },
  {
    "id": "seed-012",
    "text": "We're all just walking each other home. Some of us take the scenic route, some of us get lost, but we all end up at the same place eventually.",
    "category": "Deep",
    "timestamp": "2026-05-03T07:50:00.000Z",
    "authorId": "user-012",
    "authorName": "HopefulPanda94",
    "authorColor": "#87CEEB",
    "replyCount": 0,
    "reactionCount": 16
  }
]